nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Destiny's Way (Talking Book Publishers Inc. audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Destiny's Way is the unabridged audiobook version of the Star Wars Legends novel of the same name, by author Walter Jon Williams. The audiobook was performed by David Hartley-Margolin and released by Talking Book Publishers Inc. in 2005.
